name: The Purge #1
description:
The series is inspired by the American film The Purge: Anarchy, which revolves around a night of cleaning in all people either individually or a group of people are free to kill whoever they want without regret!I feel it doesn't make sense to happen but it's good for us to realize that killing our fellow human beings is not a good thing for whatever reason.This project I did not do alone, thanks to some of the parties who have contributed until this work was successfully created so beautifully.

Lens: Ef-S18-55mm f/4-5.6 IS STM
Camera: Cannon EOS kiss X9
Setting: ISO 100 18mm f/10 1/100 sec
